# Advanced Dynamic P&L Dashboard (Excel Power Query)

Automated Profit & Loss (P&L) dashboard built in Excel using Power Query and Pivot automation.

## Highlights
- Consolidates Actual, Budget and Last Year (LY) data from folder-based files.
- Automatically updates when new files are added to the shared folder.
- Performs YTD and variance calculations (ACT vs BUD, ACT vs LY).
- Interactive slicers for Region, Profit Center, Product and Month.
- Refreshes with one click — ensuring accuracy and eliminating manual work.

## Repository Contents
- `screenshots/` — Dashboard images (view only)
- `structure_example/` — Sample input file with headers (no real data)
- `README.md` — this file

> The full Excel model remains private. This repo demonstrates the project structure and automation logic.
